#+title: Software as a Service

* Definition
+ *Software as a Service (Saas)*
+ Users will _subscribe_ to a software only when needed rather than purchasing them.
+ This is a cheaper option if you do not always need to use a software.
* Wikipedia
:PROPERTIES:
:SOURCE:   Wikipedia
:SOURCE_LINK: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_as_a_service
:END:
+ is a *software licensing* and *delivery* model in which software is licensed on a _subscription basis_
+ It is also _centrally hosted_.
+ also known as *on-demand software*.
+ it is considered to be a part of _cloud computing_.
